 l 17 - May 22\, 2026 (6 sessions)5pm - 7:30pm$205 + $45 clay feeMaximum 10
  studentsThere will be an initial demo on throwing and trimming\, and you 
 will also receive one-on-one guidance.The class will end with learning to 
 attach a handle to a cup and glazing the cup with your chosen colors.The i
 nstructor will clear glaze your pieces once they have been bisqued at the 
 studio.Come prepared to get messy and have fun!About the Instructor: James
  Thomson has been a ceramics studio facilitator with Sebastopol Center of 
